This map is planned, detailed and build by me 
It has multiple ways to the hostages and 3 resue zones


----------------------------------------------

This map includes:

hostages!!!
custom textures 
custom models 
detail.vbsp (grass sprites on world spawn)
bot support
ambient sound (soundscapes)
sound easteregg (unfortunatly in german, sorry)
12 secret teddybear position (find them all and you deserve a cookie)
detailed appearance of a rooftop theme with 4 different house styles
rainy weather with thunder and lightning 

The map is almost bot optimized (previously they jumped in their own suicid ;) )
I tested the map with bots and optimized the map as good as I can after playing.

sorry for my english, I`m not used to write so much lately
Hope you download and enjoy!
